events.title: Info Session: Massage Therapy Info & Careers – San Diego
events.eventname: Info Session: Massage Therapy Info & Careers – San Diego
events.description:
RSVP to embark on a massage therapy career and positively impact your life, and your community!

At this online info session, you’ll get to hear more about massage therapy info and programs and find out if a career in holistic medicine is right for you. We’ll also familiarize you with the school and answer any questions you may have.

With the U.S. healthcare system currently undergoing a major scientific and philosophical evolution, patients are seeking out natural, evidence-based solutions and preventive services. This transformation is driving demand for health professionals with a passion for evidence-driven holistic healing. People are desperate for professionals who can provide innovative solutions to treat illnesses and mental health disorders, as well as promote overall well-being. The Pacific College of Health and Science massage therapy programs are uniquely positioned to help future healthcare professionals lead the holistic healthcare movement.

We look forward to meeting you virtually!

events.title: Info Session: Health and Human Performance (HHP) Programs Information
events.description:
Learn more about the Master of Science in Health and Human Performance and Health Coach Certificate

The purpose of the state-of-the-art Master of Science (Health and Human Performance) (MSHHP) is to provide students who have a deep interest in self-discovery and personal growth with the knowledge and experience required to become health and human performance coaches, and health educators.

Join an epic adventure to help clients fulfill their potential and realize their dreams

The MS in Health and Human Performance graduate applies an integrative coaching model that combines holistic and modern coaching methods, the current evidence in the physiology and psychology of performance, and whole food nutrition, as well as dietary supplementation strategies to advance health and performance in all areas of life.

Experience personal benefits while finding solutions to clients’ peak performance goals

events.title: Info Session: Holistic Nursing Programs
events.description:
Discover the Roots of Nursing Through the Prism of Holism!
Learn About the Flexible Online Programs-–From Home
  • RN to BSN Completion Program and Holistic Nursing Certificate
  • Thoughtful mixture of synchronous and asynchronous classes
  • The unique, sustainable RN to BSN program is completely online except for:
    • A 3-day retreat in NY (online option)
    • Leadership and community clinic shifts that can be done in your area
Pacific College's nursing programs change you personally and professionally and even impact your friends, family and clients. Become part of a cohort-wide support system over the course of the program. We'll cover:
  • Overviews of both programs
  • How the RN to BSN has been endorsed by the AHNCC
  • Holistic nursing’s position in today’s healthcare environment
  • The admissions process
  • Financial aid
